    "description": "<strong>目标：</strong>用Dinkys重新人口<strong>整个银河系</strong>，确保它们的<strong>安全</strong>，并<strong>完全自动化</strong>一切！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/6a45f40ddd3ad4b23a0cb2666216c486.poster.avif?t=1725190932\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/6a45f40ddd3ad4b23a0cb2666216c486.webm?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/6a45f40ddd3ad4b23a0cb2666216c486.mp4?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>克隆<strong>第一只Dinky</strong>并开始收集食物。但Dinkys并<strong>非无用</strong>，给予它们一些任务，如<strong>收集资源</strong>或<strong>制作物品</strong>。<br>借助Dinkys的帮助，扩大你的殖民地，研究新技术并建造<strong>自动化机器</strong>。<br>机器比Dinkys快得多，它们需要<strong>电力</strong>而非食物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.poster.avif?t=1725190932\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.webm?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.mp4?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>制造<strong>火箭</strong>并飞往外太空，殖民其他世界！<br>每个世界都有其自己的生物群落和不同的资源。<br>使用<strong>资源发射器</strong>在一个世界中收集资源，并将它们发送到另一个世界。<br>在多个世界之间建立你的供应链，并确保一切都在<strong>最大效</strong>率下运行！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/a489aa336c68430f4dbda56670257444.poster.avif?t=1725190932\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/a489aa336c68430f4dbda56670257444.webm?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/a489aa336c68430f4dbda56670257444.mp4?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这个世界充满了危险，<strong>Zumbys</strong>在夜间出没，它们最喜欢做的事就是吃掉Dinkys，千万不要让这种事发生！<br>使用<strong>智能地雷</strong>或配备各种<strong>弹药</strong>的塔来保护Dinkys。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/f10a8cd2ff6f80fc81b85ac2c9c78599.poster.avif?t=1725190932\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/f10a8cd2ff6f80fc81b85ac2c9c78599.webm?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/f10a8cd2ff6f80fc81b85ac2c9c78599.mp4?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >终极目标</h2>用Dinkys重新人口整个银河系，并用机器完全自动化一切，以便Dinkys可以安宁地生活！<br><br>在这个充满乐趣的殖民地建设、自动化、防御冒险游戏中，可单人游玩或与多达4名朋友一起游玩。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.poster.avif?t=1725190932\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.webm?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.mp4?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
